      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770144016975,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Deep Dives\n1. How to ensure the system executes the job\nwithin 2 secs of execution time.\n=> we have the execution table, we have workers executing \njobs, what would it take to execute the jobs within 2 secs\n\nthey should be picked and should be queued with certain\nconstraints, so that the every element in the queue gets \nexecuted under time.\n\n2 sec is a hell lot no for a cpu executing programs",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Deep Dives\n1. How to ensure the system executes the job\nwithin 2 secs of execution time.\n=> we have the execution table, we have workers executing \njobs, what would it take to execute the jobs within 2 secs\n\nthey should be picked and should be queued with certain\nconstraints, so that the every element in the queue gets \nexecuted under time.\n\n2 sec is a hell lot no for a cpu executing programs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iGdnaiLBVmZdE8q9VJ9XG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2450.59377976327,
      "y": -40.817168713372524,
      "width": 345.7197265625,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
